text:
Alexandra "Alice" Teodorescu (born 2 May 1984) is a Swedish jurist with the Företagarna organisation of Swedish entrepreneurs and a commentator on social and political issues.
Teodorescu was born in Bucharest, Romania, but came to Sweden as a child in 1989 and was raised in Lund.
She did attended the Sture Academy, a training programme for young people owned and runed by the company Timbro and named after Sture Eskilsson.
